-- Children's Place sales fall 2 percent
-- 
-- Thu Apr 9, 2009 7:50am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/09/us-childrensplace-sb-idUSTRE5382KJ20090409

 

 (Reuters) - Children's Place Retail Stores Inc reported March sales on Thursday. Highlights: 

 * March sales fell 2 percent to $156.5 million * Says net sales of $156.5 million for the five-week period ended April 4, 2009, down 2 percent * Says consolidated comparable retail sales for the fiscal month of March 2009 declined 2 * Says U.S. comparable store sales declined 3% in March 2009 * March Thomson Reuters Estimates same-store sales view was up 1 percent